      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">贴标is the Chinese term for the final labeling grade column F_LABELING.&lt;SEP&gt;A synonym for Labeling in the formulas and indicators synonym dictionary.&lt;SEP&gt;Synonym for the database field F_LABELING.</data>
