      <data key="d0">甲</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">甲is a shift in production scheduling with aliases甲班, 1班, 一班, 早班, numeric code 1, and typical time 8:00-16:00.&lt;SEP&gt;甲is a shift value with numeric equivalent 1 and aliases甲班, 1班, 一班, 早班.</data>
