    <node id="丙">
      <data key="d0">丙</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">丙is a shift in production scheduling with aliases丙班, 3班, 三班, 夜班, 晚班, numeric code 3, and typical time 0:00-8:00.&lt;SEP&gt;丙is a shift value with numeric equivalent 3 and aliases丙班, 3班, 三班, 夜班, 晚班.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-713b0902d3dd2473d8a7b6fc79cb8f47&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dff975756a76316c5e10fbb37961c3f7</data>
