    <node id="F_SHIFT">
      <data key="d0">F_SHIFT</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">F_SHIFT is a database field storing the Chinese character representation of the shift (甲, 乙, or丙).&lt;SEP&gt;Database field representing shift, with synonyms: 班次, 班次汉字.&lt;SEP&gt;F_SHIFT is the main data field representing the shift dimension in a Chinese context, with values甲, 乙, 丙and their aliases.&lt;SEP&gt;F_SHIFT is a column in the lab_intermediate_data table used for grouping shifts (甲/乙/丙).</data>
