      <data key="d0">F_LINE_NO</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">A field in the Detection Center representing the production line number, with values ranging from 1 to 4.&lt;SEP&gt;Database field representing production line number, with synonyms: 产线, 产线号, 生产线.&lt;SEP&gt;F_LINE_NO is a data field representing production line number, with Chinese aliases including产线, 产线号, 生产线, and线号.</data>
