    <node id="F_SINGLE_COIL_WEIGHT">
      <data key="d0">F_SINGLE_COIL_WEIGHT</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">A database column containing the weight of individual coils, used for summing weight in the distribution.&lt;SEP&gt;F_SINGLE_COIL_WEIGHT is the database column name for the single coil weight, stored in the lab_intermediate_data table.&lt;SEP&gt;A database column representing single coil weight used in the aggregation.&lt;SEP&gt;A database column representing the weight of a single coil, used in the SQL template.&lt;SEP&gt;F_SINGLE_COIL_WEIGHT is a column in lab_intermediate_data representing the weight of a single coil, used to compute total_weight and matched_weight.&lt;SEP&gt;A column in lab_intermediate_data representing the weight of a single coil, used for aggregation in the SQL template.&lt;SEP&gt;Column in lab_intermediate_data representing the weight of a single coil.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-957813961c6bd225bcd390b432783050&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9efcc420de21e9c640026bda07d01c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a89346ef582d2491429fb4a619ba0c4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eaa469fa109e3da0e7694dbe4aa14741&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-985990948d7ec4a2a0aaa3d3376e6d0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ffe127439929c413f3cda62f238993b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d8158b31ac0e5f48421ac68e0c0b5873</data>
