    </node>
    <node id="lab_intermediate_data">
      <data key="d0">lab_intermediate_data</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">lab_intermediate_data is a database table that stores intermediate laboratory and production data. It is used as a data source in SQL templates, specifically for calculations such as the Quality Grade Distribution. The table contains fields including F_SINGLE_COIL_WEIGHT, F_DeleteMark, F_PROD_DATE, and various judge columns, as well as information such as furnace number, production date, shift, and inspection results. This table serves as a repository for intermediate data that is queried and processed in the SQL template workflows.&lt;SEP&gt;lab_intermediate_data is a database table that serves as the data source for IntermediateData.&lt;SEP&gt;lab_intermediate_data is a database table referenced as the data source for the IntermediateData node type in kg-frontend-ontology.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-957813961c6bd225bcd390b432783050&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9efcc420de21e9c640026bda07d01c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a89346ef582d2491429fb4a619ba0c4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eaa469fa109e3da0e7694dbe4aa14741&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-985990948d7ec4a2a0aaa3d3376e6d0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ffe127439929c413f3cda62f238993b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d8158b31ac0e5f48421ac68e0c0b5873&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d010e203b3992b96293c58447c8a1796&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fe1d7f2b5553bd10b4f9332b9a99b2ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-037e2efb477dee7fd7769bfe6e4b0ea3</data>
      <data key="d4">knowledge_base.json#quality_level_distribution&lt;SEP&gt;knowledge_base.json#single_coil_weight&lt;SEP&gt;sql_templates.json#metric_aggregate&lt;SEP&gt;sql_templates.json#metric_rate&lt;SEP&gt;sql_templates.json#shift_comparison&lt;SEP&gt;sql_templates.json#daily_trend&lt;SEP&gt;sql_templates.json#unqualified_breakdown&lt;SEP&gt;sql_templates.json#detail_list&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#5. 前端 Ontology 可视化&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#1. 节点类型总览</data>
      <data key="d5">1778987010</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
