    <node id="PsLoss">
      <data key="d0">PsLoss</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">PsLoss is a technical indicator for losses, with synonyms including铁损, 磁损, 比铁损, 比损, Ps, and P.</data>
