      <data key="d0">SsPower</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">SsPower is a technical indicator for power, with synonyms including激磁功率, 视在功率, 磁化功率, Ss, and S.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d0a625cc09639410176fb4712f0e96c6</data>
      <data key="d4">aliases.json#formula</data>
