      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Thickness">
      <data key="d0">Thickness</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">Thickness is a dimensional parameter, with synonyms including厚度, 带厚, 带材厚度, and平均厚度.&lt;SEP&gt;Thickness is a column used in the formula DIFF_FIRST to compute the leftmost difference.&lt;SEP&gt;Thickness is a measurement column used as input to the DIFF_LAST formula.&lt;SEP&gt;A data column referred to in the formula for computing the minimum of a range.&lt;SEP&gt;A data attribute used in the formula for the variable.&lt;SEP&gt;Thickness is a parameter used in the formula, representing a measurement.&lt;SEP&gt;A data field representing thickness measurements, used as input for the range function in the formula.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d0a625cc09639410176fb4712f0e96c6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0d38c813d65d921fdc47047da8bea580&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b5e71c3c828b1794cd7ab677f8e4186b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-793dc28add8634f1fe7cf84b5a846318&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9b9dd172ddf40c0bdd07bbae68d11796&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a5fff8a9a17a09937473ac956f254b2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24c82aa0157addf5eedfe661109c1996</data>
