      <data key="d0">levelList</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">A parameter specifying a list of levels for filtering the judge column.&lt;SEP&gt;A parameter in the SQL template specifying a list of levels to filter the judge column.&lt;SEP&gt;levelList is a string array parameter used in the CASE condition to determine which values of judgeColumn are considered matched.&lt;SEP&gt;A parameter representing a list of level values used in the CASE condition to filter matched records.&lt;SEP&gt;A parameter providing a list of level values as strings to filter the judge column in the SQL query.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a89346ef582d2491429fb4a619ba0c4b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-eaa469fa109e3da0e7694dbe4aa14741&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-985990948d7ec4a2a0aaa3d3376e6d0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1ffe127439929c413f3cda62f238993b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d010e203b3992b96293c58447c8a1796</data>
