      <data key="d2">A parameter specifying the column used for level filtering in the query.&lt;SEP&gt;A parameter in the SQL template specifying the column used for judging.&lt;SEP&gt;judgeColumn is a column parameter used in the CASE condition to compare against levelList.&lt;SEP&gt;A parameter specifying the column name used to determine qualification status in the SQL query.&lt;SEP&gt;A parameter specifying the column used for level-based filtering in the SQL query.</data>
