    <node id="nlq-agent">
      <data key="d0">nlq-agent</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">nlq-agent is a knowledge graph and natural language query system, version 2.0 as of 2026-05-16, developed by路美实验室.&lt;SEP&gt;nlq-agent is a FastAPI microservice that provides question-answering functionality and sync endpoints for knowledge graph updates.&lt;SEP&gt;A service agent added as a proxy route and a Docker service definition.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-23fbb1625c90dbe70868caa81d311301&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6843787e11e2044bc19a86eed509efbc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c6d48945e22b6b6690ee5e93cb583f76</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#nlq-agent 开发指南&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#9. 部署与运维&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#11. 与现有代码库的集成点</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986912</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="nlq-agent Development Guide">
      <data key="d0">nlq-agent Development Guide</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
