    <node id="WrenAI">
      <data key="d0">WrenAI</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">WrenAI is an open-source project with GitHub 15k+ stars that provides a semantic layer for LLM-based SQL generation.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986326</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="路美项目">
      <data key="d0">路美项目</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">路美项目is a project that uses a knowledge graph to store business definitions for SQL generation.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986326</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="知识图谱">
      <data key="d0">知识图谱</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">知识图谱is a semantic structure in路美项目that stores business definitions including judgment rules, product specifications, and metric definitions.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986326</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="语义层">
      <data key="d0">语义层</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">语义层(Semantic Layer / MDL) is a core design concept that enables LLMs to understand business context before generating SQL.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986327</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="SQL">
      <data key="d0">SQL</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">SQL is the query language generated by the LLM and executed against the database.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986327</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="DDL">
      <data key="d0">DDL</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">DDL (Data Definition Language) is the database schema that the LLM cannot directly interpret without the semantic layer.&lt;SEP&gt;DDL (Data Definition Language) is provided to the LLM during SQL correction as context to fix the SQL.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="判定规则">
      <data key="d0">判定规则</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">判定规则stores threshold conditions for classifying products into categories, e.g., iron loss ≤ 0.80 W/kg → A class.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986327</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="指标定义">
      <data key="d0">指标定义</data>
      <data key="d1">content</data>
      <data key="d2">指标定义stores calculation formulas for statistical metrics, e.g., 合格率= (三项全合格数)/总数.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986327</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Indexing">
      <data key="d0">Indexing</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Indexing is the first stage of WrenAI's pipeline, processing data for retrieval.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986327</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Retrieval">
      <data key="d0">Retrieval</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Retrieval is the second stage of WrenAI's pipeline, fetching relevant information.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986327</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Generation">
      <data key="d0">Generation</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Generation is the third stage of WrenAI's pipeline, producing SQL queries.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986327</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="luma_rules">
      <data key="d0">luma_rules</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">luma_rules is the vector store collection where判定规则is stored.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986327</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="luma_specs">
      <data key="d0">luma_specs</data>
      <data key="d1">data</data>
      <data key="d2">luma_specs is the vector store collection where产品规格is stored.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
