    <node id="路美两阶段架构">
      <data key="d0">路美两阶段架构</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">路美两阶段架构is the architecture of路美项目, which maps from WrenAI's three-layer pipeline.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
