    </node>
    <node id="WrenAI三层Pipeline">
      <data key="d0">WrenAI三层Pipeline</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">WrenAI三层Pipeline consists of Indexing, Retrieval, and Generation stages for SQL generation.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-3e7b2af007d32a6e2000a0941bbd36f4</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#1. 架构核心思想</data>
