    </node>
    <node id="Two-Stage QA Architecture">
      <data key="d0">Two-Stage QA Architecture</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">The Two-Stage QA Architecture is the overall system design that integrates multiple agents for query processing.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5d695d3fbc263cc41744db3771835422</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#2. 两阶段问答架构</data>
