      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="FastAPI Microservice">
      <data key="d0">FastAPI Microservice</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">FastAPI Microservice is a software component located at services/agent-api that hosts and orchestrates the three agents.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5d695d3fbc263cc41744db3771835422</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#2. 两阶段问答架构</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986370</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="QueryAgent">
      <data key="d0">QueryAgent</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">QueryAgent is an agent responsible for intent classification and routing to statistical query, root cause analysis, concept explanation, or out-of-scope handling.&lt;SEP&gt;The QueryAgent is responsible for routing user queries to different agents based on intent type.&lt;SEP&gt;An agent responsible for intent classification and routing metric queries.&lt;SEP&gt;QueryAgent is an agent responsible for intent classification, routing user questions to direct answer, Chat2SQL Agent, RootCause Agent, or out-of-scope rejection.&lt;SEP&gt;QueryAgent is a software agent developed in Phase 2 for intent classification, routing, and metric query.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5d695d3fbc263cc41744db3771835422&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b513d8cfa9a77ed8608044d037739e9f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e80d481ff647b3ede0a2d805c8c73b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8edf294b6528b8f83373cbb8e01283d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#2. 两阶段问答架构&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#3. 统计问题的智能路由&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#6. 项目目录结构&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#10. 实施路线图</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986838</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="RootCause Agent">
      <data key="d0">RootCause Agent</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">RootCause Agent handles single-record root cause explanation using furnace number, detection indicators, decision formula, thresholds, specifications, and grades.&lt;SEP&gt;RootCause Agent is an agent responsible for handling root cause analysis queries.&lt;SEP&gt;RootCause Agent is a software agent developed in Phase 4 for performing root cause analysis on individual records.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5d695d3fbc263cc41744db3771835422&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8edf294b6528b8f83373cbb8e01283d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#2. 两阶段问答架构&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#10. 实施路线图</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986838</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="SSE Event Stream">
      <data key="d0">SSE Event Stream</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">SSE Event Stream is a real-time event streaming mechanism that pushes reasoning steps from the agents to the frontend component.&lt;SEP&gt;SSE Event Stream is a real-time streaming mechanism using Server-Sent Events to push reasoning steps from the `/chat/stream` endpoint.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5d695d3fbc263cc41744db3771835422&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#2. 两阶段问答架构&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="KgReasoningPanel">
      <data key="d0">KgReasoningPanel</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">KgReasoningPanel is a frontend UI component that displays the reasoning steps pushed via SSE event stream.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5d695d3fbc263cc41744db3771835422</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#2. 两阶段问答架构</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986370</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Chat2SQL Agent">
      <data key="d0">Chat2SQL Agent</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Chat2SQL Agent performs schema selection, column selection, SQL drafting, validation, execution, and result summarization.&lt;SEP&gt;An agent that converts natural language queries into SQL and executes them safely.&lt;SEP&gt;Chat2SQL Agent is an agent that handles statistical queries and is involved in SQL generation and the SQL correction loop.&lt;SEP&gt;Chat2SQL Agent is a software agent developed in Phase 3 for generating, executing, and correcting SQL queries.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5d695d3fbc263cc41744db3771835422&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e80d481ff647b3ede0a2d805c8c73b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8edf294b6528b8f83373cbb8e01283d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#2. 两阶段问答架构&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#6. 项目目录结构&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#10. 实施路线图</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986838</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Overall Architecture Diagram">
      <data key="d0">Overall Architecture Diagram</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Overall Architecture Diagram is an image file located at ../diagrams/overall_architecture.png that illustrates the two-stage QA architecture system.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5d695d3fbc263cc41744db3771835422</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#2. 两阶段问答架构</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986370</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="QueryAgent File">
      <data key="d0">QueryAgent File</data>
