    <node id="Qdrant">
      <data key="d0">Qdrant</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">A vector database used to store vectorized natural language text of the semantic layer data.&lt;SEP&gt;A vector database service used for embedding storage and retrieval, orchestrated in docker-compose.&lt;SEP&gt;Qdrant is a vector database service that stores and searches embeddings. It is deployed as a container and exposes REST and gRPC APIs.&lt;SEP&gt;Qdrant is a vector database deployed in Phase 1 as part of semantic layer infrastructure.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-6a6cdc66d52ec10ea8f88d70678018b0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7e80d481ff647b3ede0a2d805c8c73b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6843787e11e2044bc19a86eed509efbc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f8edf294b6528b8f83373cbb8e01283d</data>
