    <node id="Ribbon">
      <data key="d0">Ribbon</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Ribbon is the root node of the front-end ontology knowledge graph, serving as the starting point for force-directed layout expansion.&lt;SEP&gt;A node type in kg-frontend-ontology representing material strip (display name: 带材), data source: 虚拟根节点, size 110×110, colors #E6F4FF background and #1677FF border.&lt;SEP&gt;Ribbon is the business root node in the domain ontology, with ID domain:ribbon. It serves as the entry point for furnace numbers, connecting specifications, detection data, formulas, and judgment rules.&lt;SEP&gt;Ribbon is a data entity in the ontology that contains ProductSpec, imports via RawDataImport and MagneticDataImport, and has identifier FurnaceNoInput.&lt;SEP&gt;A trigger node for the RibbonRoot panel, representing a ribbon UI element.&lt;SEP&gt;Ribbon is a node type in the ontology that is included in the ACTIVE_NODE_TYPES whitelist.&lt;SEP&gt;A node type planned to have a relationship with AppearanceFeature via HAS_APPEARANCE.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fe1d7f2b5553bd10b4f9332b9a99b2ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-037e2efb477dee7fd7769bfe6e4b0ea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5c50f730a0f56b891af722a89e9a544&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a57a8741ef32619b74072e5c073f6eab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36916be8986716ed209d412539919743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c891a5798f8f62f082839f1a25296489&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-49c808df8cd65618a6d171acea6fbbda</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#5. 前端 Ontology 可视化&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#1. 节点类型总览&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#2. 节点详细规格&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#3. 连接关系（Palantir Ontology 命名）&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#4. 面板类型规格&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#6. 前端渲染白名单&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#8. 待构建节点（后续步骤）</data>
      <data key="d5">1778987429</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="ProductSpec">
      <data key="d0">ProductSpec</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">ProductSpec is a node type within a knowledge graph, representing product specifications at the L2 product layer. Its data source is the `lab_product_spec` table. In the kg-frontend-ontology, the node is displayed with the name "产品规格" (product specification), has dimensions of 90×90 pixels, and uses a background color of #F0F5FF with a border color of #2F54EB.

Each ProductSpec instance is uniquely identified by the key `spec:{F_Id}`. It is a child of the Ribbon node through a "contains" relationship and, in turn, owns or is associated with SpecAttribute nodes, which store the attributes of the specification. ProductSpec also serves as a trigger node for the Spec panel, linking to product specification data. Additionally, it is included in the `ACTIVE_NODE_TYPES` whitelist within the ontology.&lt;SEP&gt;A node type planned to have a relationship with JudgmentRule via HAS_RULE.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fe1d7f2b5553bd10b4f9332b9a99b2ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f9301c28a60e02d9a6907aada6663783&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-037e2efb477dee7fd7769bfe6e4b0ea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5c50f730a0f56b891af722a89e9a544&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a57a8741ef32619b74072e5c073f6eab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36916be8986716ed209d412539919743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c891a5798f8f62f082839f1a25296489&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-49c808df8cd65618a6d171acea6fbbda</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#5. 前端 Ontology 可视化&lt;SEP&gt;docs/development-guide.md#8. Neo4j 知识图谱&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#1. 节点类型总览&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#2. 节点详细规格&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#3. 连接关系（Palantir Ontology 命名）&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#4. 面板类型规格&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#6. 前端渲染白名单&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#8. 待构建节点（后续步骤）</data>
      <data key="d5">1778987429</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="RawDataImport">
      <data key="d0">RawDataImport</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">RawDataImport represents stacking data at the L2 data layer, with data source lab_raw_data.&lt;SEP&gt;A node type in kg-frontend-ontology representing lamination data (display name: 叠片数据), data source: lab_raw_data, size 95×95, colors #ECFDF5 background and #10B981 border.&lt;SEP&gt;RawDataImport is a node representing imported raw data for lamination, identified by tmpl:{F_Id} (template ID). It is a child of Ribbon via importsVia relationship. Its target data table is lab_raw_data.&lt;SEP&gt;RawDataImport is a data entity representing raw data import, used by Ribbon for importing and producing IntermediateData.&lt;SEP&gt;A trigger node for the Spec panel, related to raw data import.&lt;SEP&gt;RawDataImport is a node type in the ontology that is included in the ACTIVE_NODE_TYPES whitelist.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fe1d7f2b5553bd10b4f9332b9a99b2ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-037e2efb477dee7fd7769bfe6e4b0ea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5c50f730a0f56b891af722a89e9a544&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a57a8741ef32619b74072e5c073f6eab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36916be8986716ed209d412539919743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c891a5798f8f62f082839f1a25296489</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#5. 前端 Ontology 可视化&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#1. 节点类型总览&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#2. 节点详细规格&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#3. 连接关系（Palantir Ontology 命名）&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#4. 面板类型规格&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#6. 前端渲染白名单</data>
      <data key="d5">1778987329</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="MagneticDataImport">
      <data key="d0">MagneticDataImport</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">MagneticDataImport represents single-piece performance data at the L2 data layer, with data source lab_magnetic_raw_data.&lt;SEP&gt;A node type in kg-frontend-ontology representing single piece performance (display name: 单片性能), data source: lab_magnetic_raw_data, size 95×95, colors #FEF3C7 background and #F59E0B border.&lt;SEP&gt;MagneticDataImport is a node representing imported magnetic data for single pieces. It is a child of Ribbon via importsVia relationship. No further details provided.&lt;SEP&gt;MagneticDataImport is a data entity representing magnetic data import, used by Ribbon for importing and referencing furnace number nodes.&lt;SEP&gt;A trigger node for the Spec panel, related to magnetic data import.&lt;SEP&gt;MagneticDataImport is a node type in the ontology that is included in the ACTIVE_NODE_TYPES whitelist.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fe1d7f2b5553bd10b4f9332b9a99b2ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-037e2efb477dee7fd7769bfe6e4b0ea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5c50f730a0f56b891af722a89e9a544&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a57a8741ef32619b74072e5c073f6eab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36916be8986716ed209d412539919743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c891a5798f8f62f082839f1a25296489</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#5. 前端 Ontology 可视化&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#1. 节点类型总览&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#2. 节点详细规格&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#3. 连接关系（Palantir Ontology 命名）&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#4. 面板类型规格&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#6. 前端渲染白名单</data>
      <data key="d5">1778987329</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="FurnaceNoInput">
      <data key="d0">FurnaceNoInput</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">FurnaceNoInput is an L2 identification layer node for furnace number input, using furnace number parsing rules.&lt;SEP&gt;A node type in kg-frontend-ontology representing raw furnace number (display name: 原始炉号), data source: furnace number parsing rules (炉号解析规则), size 90×90, colors #FEF3C7 background and #D97706 border.&lt;SEP&gt;FurnaceNoInput is a node representing the original furnace number input. It is a child of Ribbon via hasIdentifier relationship. No further details provided.&lt;SEP&gt;FurnaceNoInput is a data entity representing a furnace number input, identified by Ribbon and parsed to FurnaceNoParsed.&lt;SEP&gt;A trigger node for the FurnaceNo panel, related to furnace number input.&lt;SEP&gt;FurnaceNoInput is a node type in the ontology that is included in the ACTIVE_NODE_TYPES whitelist.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fe1d7f2b5553bd10b4f9332b9a99b2ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-037e2efb477dee7fd7769bfe6e4b0ea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5c50f730a0f56b891af722a89e9a544&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a57a8741ef32619b74072e5c073f6eab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36916be8986716ed209d412539919743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c891a5798f8f62f082839f1a25296489</data>
