    </node>
    <node id="FurnaceNoParsed">
      <data key="d0">FurnaceNoParsed</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">FurnaceNoParsed is an L2 identification layer node for parsed furnace number, using furnace number parsing rules.&lt;SEP&gt;A node type in kg-frontend-ontology representing parsed furnace number (display name: 炉号), data source: furnace number parsing rules (炉号解析规则), size 85×85, colors #ECFDF5 background and #059669 border.&lt;SEP&gt;FurnaceNoParsed is a data entity representing a parsed furnace number, having FurnaceNoField as component.&lt;SEP&gt;A trigger node for the FurnaceNo panel, related to parsed furnace number.&lt;SEP&gt;FurnaceNoParsed is a node type in the ontology that is included in the ACTIVE_NODE_TYPES whitelist.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fe1d7f2b5553bd10b4f9332b9a99b2ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-037e2efb477dee7fd7769bfe6e4b0ea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a57a8741ef32619b74072e5c073f6eab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36916be8986716ed209d412539919743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c891a5798f8f62f082839f1a25296489</data>
