    </node>
    <node id="SpecAttribute">
      <data key="d0">SpecAttribute</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">SpecAttribute represents extended attributes at the L3 attribute layer, with data source lab_product_spec_attribute.&lt;SEP&gt;Spec extension attribute entity in the knowledge graph, representing attributes from the lab_product_spec_attribute table.&lt;SEP&gt;Spec extension attribute entity in the knowledge graph, representing attributes from the lab_product_spec_attribute table.&lt;SEP&gt;A node type in kg-frontend-ontology representing product attribute (display name: 产品属性), data source: lab_product_spec_attribute, size 85×85, colors #FFF0F6 background and #EB2F96 border.&lt;SEP&gt;SpecAttribute is a node representing extended product attributes, identified by attr:{F_ATTRIBUTE_KEY} or attr:{F_ATTRIBUTE_NAME}. It is a child of ProductSpec via hasAttribute relationship. Its data source is the lab_product_spec_attribute table.&lt;SEP&gt;SpecAttribute is a concept representing an attribute of a product specification, owned by ProductSpec.&lt;SEP&gt;SpecAttribute is a node type in the ontology that is included in the ACTIVE_NODE_TYPES whitelist.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fe1d7f2b5553bd10b4f9332b9a99b2ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f9301c28a60e02d9a6907aada6663783&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-037e2efb477dee7fd7769bfe6e4b0ea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c5c50f730a0f56b891af722a89e9a544&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a57a8741ef32619b74072e5c073f6eab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c891a5798f8f62f082839f1a25296489</data>
