      <data key="d5">1778987329</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="TemplateField">
      <data key="d0">TemplateField</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">TemplateField represents table fields at the L3 field layer, with data source INFORMATION_SCHEMA.COLUMNS.&lt;SEP&gt;A node type in kg-frontend-ontology representing field mapping (display name: 字段映射), data source: various tables (INFORMATION_SCHEMA.COLUMNS), size 70×70, colors #F3F4F6 background and #9CA3AF border.&lt;SEP&gt;TemplateField is a concept representing a field within an import template or intermediate data.&lt;SEP&gt;A trigger node for the Spec panel, related to template fields.&lt;SEP&gt;TemplateField is a node type in the ontology that is included in the ACTIVE_NODE_TYPES whitelist.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fe1d7f2b5553bd10b4f9332b9a99b2ef&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-037e2efb477dee7fd7769bfe6e4b0ea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a57a8741ef32619b74072e5c073f6eab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-36916be8986716ed209d412539919743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c891a5798f8f62f082839f1a25296489</data>
