      <data key="d0">IntermediateData</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">IntermediateData represents intermediate calculation data at the L3 calculation layer, with data source lab_intermediate_data.&lt;SEP&gt;A node type in kg-frontend-ontology representing intermediate data (display name: 中间数据), data source: lab_intermediate_data, size 90×90, colors #E0F2FE background and #0EA5E9 border.&lt;SEP&gt;IntermediateData is a data entity produced by RawDataImport.&lt;SEP&gt;A trigger node for the Spec panel, related to intermediate data.&lt;SEP&gt;IntermediateData is a node type in the ontology that is included in the ACTIVE_NODE_TYPES whitelist.</data>
