    <node id="User Question">
      <data key="d0">User Question</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">User Question is the input that enters the agent orchestration pipeline and is classified by QueryAgent.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Direct Answer">
      <data key="d0">Direct Answer</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Direct Answer is the response given by QueryAgent for conceptual queries, skipping SQL generation.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="OutOfScope Response">
      <data key="d0">OutOfScope Response</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">OutOfScope Response is the rejection response given by QueryAgent for out-of-scope queries.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="LangGraph State Machine">
      <data key="d0">LangGraph State Machine</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">LangGraph State Machine is defined in `app/agents/graph.py` and manages the agent orchestration flow.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="app/agents/graph.py">
      <data key="d0">app/agents/graph.py</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">app/agents/graph.py is a file that defines the LangGraph State Machine and agent orchestration logic.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="SQL Security Mechanism">
      <data key="d0">SQL Security Mechanism</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">SQL Security Mechanism is implemented in `app/tools/sql_tools.py` and includes three layers: regex whitelist, AST validation, and automatic LIMIT.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Regular Expression Whitelist">
      <data key="d0">Regular Expression Whitelist</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Regular Expression Whitelist is the first layer of SQL security that only allows SELECT statements, blocking all write operations.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="AST Validation">
      <data key="d0">AST Validation</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">AST Validation is the second layer of SQL security that parses SQL AST to prohibit subqueries with write operations and dangerous functions.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Automatic LIMIT">
      <data key="d0">Automatic LIMIT</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Automatic LIMIT is the third layer of SQL security that appends LIMIT 501 if no LIMIT clause is present, truncating results beyond 500 rows.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="app/tools/sql_tools.py">
      <data key="d0">app/tools/sql_tools.py</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">app/tools/sql_tools.py is a file that implements the three-layer SQL security mechanism.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="SQL Correction Loop">
      <data key="d0">SQL Correction Loop</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">SQL Correction Loop is a process where Chat2SQL Agent retries SQL execution up to two times with LLM assistance when the initial SQL fails.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="app/api/chat.py">
      <data key="d0">app/api/chat.py</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">app/api/chat.py is a file that implements the SSE Event Stream endpoint `/chat/stream`.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-e376f7f6a81dd4706f50d07a152fe75d</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/development-guide.md#7. 关键代码设计详解</data>
      <data key="d5">1778986665</data>
