    <node id="Semantic Layer Initialization">
      <data key="d0">Semantic Layer Initialization</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Semantic Layer Initialization is a startup step that loads the knowledge graph schema into the semantic layer.&lt;SEP&gt;Semantic Layer Initialization is the process of running the semantic layer setup with Qdrant, TEI, and Neo4j in Phase 1.</data>
