    <node id="kg-frontend-ontology">
      <data key="d0">kg-frontend-ontology</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">kg-frontend-ontology is a specification document that describes node types, data sources, connection relationships, and panel display rules for the frontend knowledge graph component relation-graph-vue3. It corresponds to backend API GET /api/v1/kg/ontology and was last updated on 2026-05-16.&lt;SEP&gt;An ontology for frontend knowledge graph, containing node types with display names, data sources, sizes, and colors, and using force-directed layout with nodeShape 0 and borderRadius 50%.&lt;SEP&gt;kg-frontend-ontology is a software project defining the frontend ontology for a knowledge graph, including a backend data interface.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-9e6fbeee96d870f3f22dbe7072d90982&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-037e2efb477dee7fd7769bfe6e4b0ea3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-80ce63a4f0eed6e06bad7bdd88ec9a05</data>
      <data key="d4">docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#知识图谱前端 Ontology 规格文档&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#1. 节点类型总览&lt;SEP&gt;docs/kg-frontend-ontology.md#5. 后端数据接口</data>
      <data key="d5">1778987285</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
