    <node id="Formula Type 1">
      <data key="d0">Formula Type 1</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Formula Type 1 is the value of the formulaType field, indicating that the formula used is DIFF_LAST.&lt;SEP&gt;A numeric code indicating the type of formula used, with value 1 as specified in the input.</data>
