    <node id="前部平均值">
      <data key="d0">前部平均值</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">前部平均值is a computed average value for a front portion, defined by a formula involving a range over Detection values from 1 to 5, with unit in micrometers.</data>
